# Design System Rules

Before building any page, define the complete design system as CSS custom properties in `:root`. Never hardcode raw values in component CSS — always consume tokens.

## Required token groups

### Colors (light + dark values for each role)

- `--color-primary` (+ `-hover`, `-active`, `-soft`)
- `--color-secondary`
- `--color-accent`
- `--color-success`, `--color-warning`, `--color-error` (+ `-soft` surfaces for banners/badges)
- `--color-bg` (page background), `--color-surface` (cards/panels), `--color-surface-2` (nested)
- `--color-text`, `--color-text-muted`, `--color-border`
- All text/background pairs must meet WCAG AA contrast: 4.5:1 body text, 3:1 large text and UI components

### Typography

- Font stacks: prefer system stack (`--font-sans`, optional `--font-display`); if a webfont is essential, embed via `@font-face` with `font-display: swap` — never a render-blocking `<link>`
- Scale (fluid with `clamp()`):
  - `--text-display` (~clamp(2.5rem, 5vw + 1rem, 4.5rem))
  - `--text-h1`, `--text-h2`, `--text-h3` (headings)
  - `--text-subheading`
  - `--text-body` (1rem), `--text-sm`, `--text-caption` (0.75–0.8125rem)
- Line heights: `--leading-tight` (1.1–1.2 display/headings), `--leading-normal` (1.5–1.7 body)
- Weights: `--font-regular: 400`, `--font-medium: 500`, `--font-semibold: 600`, `--font-bold: 700`

### Spacing scale (px values, expressed in rem)

`--space-1: 0.25rem` (4) · `--space-2: 0.5rem` (8) · `--space-3: 0.75rem` (12) · `--space-4: 1rem` (16) · `--space-6: 1.5rem` (24) · `--space-8: 2rem` (32) · `--space-12: 3rem` (48) · `--space-16: 4rem` (64) · `--space-24: 6rem` (96)

### Radius

`--radius-sm: 6px` · `--radius-md: 10px` · `--radius-lg: 16px` · `--radius-xl: 24px` · `--radius-full: 9999px`

### Shadows

`--shadow-sm`, `--shadow-md`, `--shadow-lg`, `--shadow-xl` — layered, low-opacity shadows; adjust opacity for dark mode (shadows nearly invisible on dark surfaces; prefer borders/elevation color shifts)

### Grid and layout

- `--container-max: 72rem` (1152px) default; `--container-wide: 80rem` for ultra-wide sections
- `.container` utility: `width: min(100% - 2 * var(--space-4), var(--container-max)); margin-inline: auto;`
- 12-column mental model implemented with CSS Grid (`grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr)` or `auto-fit/minmax` for card grids)

### Breakpoints (min-width)

`--bp-sm: 640px` · `--bp-md: 768px` · `--bp-lg: 1024px` · `--bp-xl: 1280px` · `--bp-2xl: 1536px`
(Media queries cannot use custom properties — document these as comments and use the raw values consistently.)

### Motion

- Durations: `--duration-fast: 150ms`, `--duration-base: 250ms`, `--duration-slow: 400ms`
- Easings: `--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)`, `--ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.35, 1)`
- Reveal distance: `--reveal-distance: 24px`
- Every animation must be disabled or reduced under `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)`

## Dark mode

- Default theme chosen by `prefers-color-scheme`; explicit override via `[data-theme="light"|"dark"]` on `<html>`, toggled by JS and persisted to `localStorage`
- Only token values change between themes — component CSS never branches on theme
